Package net.jqwik.time.api.constraints

Annotation Type YearMonthRange

  • @Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,PARAMETER,TYPE_USE})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Documented
@API(status=EXPERIMENTAL,
     since="1.4.0")
public @interface YearMonthRange
    Constrain the range of generated year and month parameters.

    Applies to YearMonth parameters which are also annotated with @ForAll.

    See Also:
    ForAll, DateRange, DayOfMonthRange, DayOfWeekRange, MonthDayRange, MonthRange, YearRange
